### 修改学生名字
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/students/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Yixuan Zhang"
}

### 查询所有学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students

### 查询所有课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses

{
  "count": 2,
  "items": [
    { "id": 1, "code": "CCST9017", "title": "Hidden Order in Daily Life: A Mathematical Perspective" },
    { "id": 2, "code": "COMP1117", "title": "Computer Programming" }
  ]
}

### 修改课程：需要編號，课程代码和名称
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/courses/_
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "______",
  "title": "________"
}

### 添加一门新课程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "FINA2320",
  "title": "Investments and portfolio analysis"
}

### 添加一名新学生
POST http://localhost:8080/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zihao Zhao"
}

### 给学生 6 添加课程 3
POST http://localhost:8080/api/students/6/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course_id": 1
}

### 删除学生 1 的课程 3
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/students/1/courses/3
